Give Shoppers More Options with Coupons at Checkout
This change applies to D2C Commerce in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions.
New D2C stores have the Promotions component included on the checkout page. If you have an existing store, use one of the preset checkout layouts that includes the Promotions component.
